<section class="sect" id="use-cases">
  <div class="wrap">
    <p class="sect-eyebrow" data-reveal>Who It Is For</p>
    <h2 class="sect-heading" data-reveal>Two buyer stories matter: the Rails developer and the Rails team.</h2>

    <div class="cases" data-stagger>
      <article class="case">
        <p class="case-kicker">Solo Rails dev</p>
        <h3 class="case-title">Fewer tool boundaries, faster feedback.</h3>
        <p class="case-copy">Install gems, inspect dependencies, run tasks, and jump into Rails commands without bouncing between unrelated CLIs.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="case">
        <p class="case-kicker">Platform or app team</p>
        <h3 class="case-title">A better default story for Docker and CI.</h3>
        <p class="case-copy">Use a single binary-oriented path for diagnostics, cache strategy, task orchestration, and a cleaner packaging story around dependency workflows.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="case">
        <p class="case-kicker">Ruby-curious adopters</p>
        <h3 class="case-title">The “Bun for Ruby” mental model.</h3>
        <p class="case-copy">You keep familiar verbs, but the product promise is modern startup time, aggressive parsing performance, and a CLI that feels intentionally designed.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .sect {
    padding: var(--sp-24) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .sect-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .sect-heading {
    font-size: clamp(var(--text-2xl), 4vw, var(--text-3xl));
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.15;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-12);
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .cases {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--sp-4);
  }

  .case {
    padding: var(--sp-6);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(171, 27, 51, 0.08), transparent 24%), var(--bg-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
  }

  .case-kicker {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: #ffdbe1;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }

  .case-title {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: 1.35;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }

  .case-copy {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--fg-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @media (max-width: 960px) {
    .cases {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
